Module camp_management_and_application_system

Package model.camp

package model.camp
This subpackage contains classes for camps
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Camp
    Represents a camp declared within the system Each camp has various attributes such as a unique identifier, name, closing date, available schools, location, time slots, camp committee slots, camp description, staff in charge, list of attendees and committee members, and withdrawn participants.
    Enquiry
    This Enquiry Class represent inquiry related to a camp.
    Suggestion
    This class Suggestion is related to camp within the system Suggestions are made by committee member and can be approaved or reject by staff in charge for the camp.
